| 新客户询盘回复 | (直接用 /inquiry) | — | — |
| 大批量客户分析 | brainstorming | writing-plans | to-prd |
| 单个客户跟进 | (直接用 OKKI 框架) | — | — |
| 复杂多款式报价 | brainstorming | — | — |
| 模糊需求 | grill-me | brainstorming | writing-plans |
| OKKI 脚本报错 | systematic-debugging | — | — |
| 改进 ECC 技能 | writing-skills | — | — |
| 月度运营报告 | writing-plans | to-prd | — |
